{"data":[{"name":"80:1","price":"1 Le visage renfrogné, il s’est détourné","arabic":"عَبَسَ وَتَوَلَّىٰٓ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5759,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"80:2","price":"2 de l’aveugle qui était venu l’interroger[1546].","arabic":"أَن جَآءَهُ ٱلۡأَعۡمَىٰ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5760,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"[1546] Interroger le Prophète, en pleine discussion avec un ou plusieurs notables de la Mecque dont il désirait gagner le cœur. Certains voient, à raison d’ailleurs, dans ces reproches adressés au Prophète par son Seigneur l’une des preuves les plus évidentes de l’authenticité du Coran et de la mission du Messager.","lang":"fr"},{"name":"80:3","price":"3 Qu’en sais-tu ? Tes paroles l’aideront peut-être à se purifier[1547]","arabic":"وَمَا يُدۡرِيكَ لَعَلَّهُۥ يَزَّكَّىٰٓ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5761,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"[1547] A purifier son âme.","lang":"fr"},{"name":"80:4","price":"4 et il se peut que tes exhortations lui soient d’une grande utilité.","arabic":"أَوۡ يَذَّكَّرُ فَتَنفَعَهُ ٱلذِّكۡرَىٰٓ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5762,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"80:5","price":"5 Quant à celui qui croit pouvoir se passer de la vérité,","arabic":"أَمَّا مَنِ ٱسۡتَغۡنَىٰ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5763,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"80:6","price":"6 tu n’hésites pas à aller à sa rencontre pour lui parler.","arabic":"فَأَنتَ لَهُۥ تَصَدَّىٰ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5764,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"80:7","price":"7 Or, tu n’auras pas à répondre de son refus de se purifier[1548].","arabic":"وَمَا عَلَيۡكَ أَلَّا يَزَّكَّىٰ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5765,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"[1548] De l’impiété.","lang":"fr"},{"name":"80:8","price":"8 Mais celui qui s’empresse vers toi,","arabic":"وَأَمَّا مَن جَآءَكَ يَسۡعَىٰ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5766,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"80:9","price":"9 poussé par la seule crainte d’Allah,","arabic":"وَهُوَ يَخۡشَىٰ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5767,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"80:10","price":"10 tu ne te soucies guère de son cas !","arabic":"فَأَنتَ عَنۡهُ تَلَهَّىٰ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5768,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"80:11","price":"11 N’agis plus ainsi ! Voici une exhortation","arabic":"كَلَّآ إِنَّهَا تَذۡكِرَةٞ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5769,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"80:12","price":"12 - que celui qui le veut en tire des leçons -","arabic":"فَمَن شَآءَ ذَكَرَهُۥ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5770,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"80:13","price":"13 consignée dans des feuillets en grand honneur[1549],","arabic":"فِي صُحُفٖ مُّكَرَّمَةٖ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5771,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"[1549] Auprès du Seigneur.","lang":"fr"},{"name":"80:14","price":"14 soigneusement préservés et d’une très haute valeur,","arabic":"مَّرۡفُوعَةٖ مُّطَهَّرَةِۭ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5772,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"80:15","price":"15 entre les mains de scribes, de nobles ambassadeurs[1550],","arabic":"بِأَيۡدِي سَفَرَةٖ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5773,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"[1550] Entre Allah et les hommes, c’est-à-dire, les anges.","lang":"fr"},{"name":"80:16","price":"16 en honneur auprès d’Allah, obéissant en tout à leur Seigneur.","arabic":"كِرَامِۭ بَرَرَةٖ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5774,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"80:17","price":"17 Que l’homme soit maudit ! Comme il est ingrat et impie[1551] ! ","arabic":"قُتِلَ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ مَآ أَكۡفَرَهُۥ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5775,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"[1551] Autre sens : qu’est-ce qui l’a poussé à tant d’ingratitude et d’impiété ?","lang":"fr"},{"name":"80:18","price":"18 Ne sait-il donc pas de quoi le Seigneur l’a créé ?","arabic":"مِنۡ أَيِّ شَيۡءٍ خَلَقَهُۥ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5776,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"80:19","price":"19 D’un liquide insignifiant qu’Il a transformé à Son gré,","arabic":"مِن نُّطۡفَةٍ خَلَقَهُۥ فَقَدَّرَهُۥ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5777,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"80:20","price":"20 avant de lui indiquer clairement la voie du salut.","arabic":"ثُمَّ ٱلسَّبِيلَ يَسَّرَهُۥ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5778,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"80:21","price":"21 Puis Il le fera mourir et mettre au tombeau.","arabic":"ثُمَّ أَمَاتَهُۥ فَأَقۡبَرَهُۥ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5779,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"80:22","price":"22 Et lorsqu’Il le voudra, Il le ressuscitera. ","arabic":"ثُمَّ إِذَا شَآءَ أَنشَرَهُۥ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5780,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"80:23","price":"23 Mais Allah n’a pas encore exécuté Son arrêt[1552]. ","arabic":"كَلَّا لَمَّا يَقۡضِ مَآ أَمَرَهُۥ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5781,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"[1552] Relatif à la Résurrection. Autre sens : l’homme refuse pourtant d’exécuter les ordres du Seigneur. ","lang":"fr"},{"name":"80:24","price":"24 Que l’homme considère d’où lui vient sa nourriture,","arabic":"فَلۡيَنظُرِ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ إِلَىٰ طَعَامِهِۦٓ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5782,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"80:25","price":"25 comment Nous répandons, du ciel, une pluie abondante","arabic":"أَنَّا صَبَبۡنَا ٱلۡمَآءَ صَبّٗا","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5783,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"80:26","price":"26 sur la terre qui se fend pour laisser surgir diverses plantes.","arabic":"ثُمَّ شَقَقۡنَا ٱلۡأَرۡضَ شَقّٗا","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5784,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"80:27","price":"27 Nous y faisons ainsi pousser toutes sortes de céréales,","arabic":"فَأَنۢبَتۡنَا فِيهَا حَبّٗا","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5785,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"80:28","price":"28 de même que des vignes et des herbages,","arabic":"وَعِنَبٗا وَقَضۡبٗا","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5786,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"80:29","price":"29 différentes variétés d’oliviers et de dattiers, ","arabic":"وَزَيۡتُونٗا وَنَخۡلٗا","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5787,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"80:30","price":"30 des jardins luxuriants aux arbres imposants,","arabic":"وَحَدَآئِقَ غُلۡبٗا","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5788,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"80:31","price":"31 ainsi que des fruits variés et des pâturages,","arabic":"وَفَٰكِهَةٗ وَأَبّٗا","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5789,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"80:32","price":"32 pour votre jouissance et celle de vos bestiaux.","arabic":"مَّتَٰعٗا لَّكُمۡ وَلِأَنۡعَٰمِكُمۡ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5790,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"80:33","price":"33 Mais lorsque retentira le Cri assourdissant,","arabic":"فَإِذَا جَآءَتِ ٱلصَّآخَّةُ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5791,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"80:34","price":"34 ce Jour-là, l’homme fuira son frère,","arabic":"يَوۡمَ يَفِرُّ ٱلۡمَرۡءُ مِنۡ أَخِيهِ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5792,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"80:35","price":"35 de même que sa mère et son père,","arabic":"وَأُمِّهِۦ وَأَبِيهِ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5793,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"80:36","price":"36 mais aussi sa compagne et ses enfants,","arabic":"وَصَٰحِبَتِهِۦ وَبَنِيهِ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5794,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"80:37","price":"37 chacun étant suffisamment préoccupé par son sort.","arabic":"لِكُلِّ ٱمۡرِيٕٖ مِّنۡهُمۡ يَوۡمَئِذٖ شَأۡنٞ يُغۡنِيهِ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5795,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"80:38","price":"38 Ce Jour-là, certains visages seront rayonnants,","arabic":"وُجُوهٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ مُّسۡفِرَةٞ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5796,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"80:39","price":"39 totalement épanouis et remplis de joie,","arabic":"ضَاحِكَةٞ مُّسۡتَبۡشِرَةٞ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5797,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"80:40","price":"40 tandis que d’autres seront poussiéreux,","arabic":"وَوُجُوهٞ يَوۡمَئِذٍ عَلَيۡهَا غَبَرَةٞ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5798,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"80:41","price":"41 couverts d’opprobre et enveloppés de ténèbres,","arabic":"تَرۡهَقُهَا قَتَرَةٌ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5799,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"80:42","price":"42 les visages de ceux qui vivaient dans l’impiété et le péché.","arabic":"أُوْلَٰٓئِكَ هُمُ ٱلۡكَفَرَةُ ٱلۡفَجَرَةُ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5800,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"}],"chapter":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa","Chapter Abasa","Surah 80","Chapter 80","He Frowned","عبس"]}